headline: DuPont Board of Directors Approves Qnity Distribution
summary: DuPont (NYSE: DD) today announced that its Board of Directors has approved the previously announced separation of its Electronics business, Qnity Electronics, Inc. ("Qnity"). To effect the separation, the DuPont Board of Directors declared a pro rata dividend of all of the issued and outstanding shares of common stock of Qnity.
